#  pyrop

## Overview

Imperative-style railway-oriented programming in Python

## Getting Started

Install `pyrop`:

```
pip install pyrop
```

A simple example:

```python
import pyrop

# Do something with pyrop
```

See a
[more in-depth tutorial here.](
https://nickderobertis.github.io/pyrop/tutorial.html
)

## Links

See the
[documentation here.](
https://nickderobertis.github.io/pyrop/
